| Ca | Moderate, Ca(OH)₂ + H₂ | - |
| Mg | Very slow | MgO + H₂ (heated) |
| Zn | No reaction | ZnO + H₂ (heated strongly) |
| Fe | No reaction | Fe₃O₄ + H₂ (heated strongly) |

